Domino is a synthetic-data generator, used to train an ensemble of decentralized, in-browser AI models at https://src.eco. Connect your computer to the swarm, and help us discover more-efficient ways to compute things.

Experiment with a curated selection of modern language models; adjust their hyperparameters, or play with an atomic simulation drawn to your screen. Domino will passively run in the background, borrowing CPU cycles from your device, and use them to perform AI inference.

Because it's not about the quality of data; it's about quantity.
